{"word":"G5246 - ὑπέρογκος - hypéronkos - hoop-er'-ong-kos - Great swelling","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπέρογκος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypéronkos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-er'-ong-kos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Great swelling</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"வீண் வார்த்தைகளான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"overswollen; immoderate, extravagant"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5228 - ὑπέρ - hypér - hoop-er'/5228\">G5228</a> and <a href=\"#/G3591 - ὄγκος - ónkos - ong'-kos/3591\">G3591</a>; <i>bulging over</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>insolent:</i> - great swelling.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}